Things to be done to get a v0.1 up and working :

1. USART

	* Use interrupt-driven serial communications

2. Multitasking

	* Allow use of interrupts, and allow tasks to sleep while waiting for an interrupt

3. Keyboard

	* Implement PS/2 protocol using USART
	
4. File System

	* Write EEPROM drivers
	* Design & implement simple file system

5. Interactive shell

	* Write simple interactive shell to be used through the serial connection
